ies ~50 files across `apps/phaser3/src/ui/`, `designs/issue-19/`, and documentat
ion.\n\n2. **Core changes for issue-19 (UIPanel, UIDialog, UIToast, UIAlert)**:\
n   - UIPanel: Added show/hide animations, overlay support, close button with UI
Icon, depth management\n   - UIDialog: Now inherits UIPanel, adds confirm/cancel
buttons, static factory methods\n   - UIToast: Simplified to pure message toast,
added left color bar, ToastManager singleton\n   - UIAlert: Added left color bar
, removed Unicode icons, show/hide animations\n\n3. **Issues found**:\n\n   **Bl
ocking issues:**\n   - None that would make the code non-functional\n\n   **Majo
r issues:**\n   - Magic number colors outside `utils.ts`: `UIDialog.ts:109` uses
