5, only utils.ts should contain hex color literals. The PRD-004 and design-spec 
explicitly require no magic number color values outside utils.ts.\n   - `UIScrol
lView.ts` uses `0xffffff` and `0x333333` as magic numbers\n   - `UIResourceDispl
ay.ts` uses `0xffffff` and `#aaaaaa` as magic numbers\n   - `UIAvatar.ts` uses `
#ffffff` hardcoded\n   - `UIProgressBar.ts` uses `#ffffff` hardcoded\n   - `UIIc
onButton.ts` uses `#ffffff` hardcoded\n   - `UIInput.ts` uses `#2c2c2c` and `#99
9999` hardcoded\n   - `UITooltip.ts` uses `#ffffff` and `#cccccc` hardcoded\n   
- `UIText.ts` uses `#ffffff` and `#000000` hardcoded\n\n   Wait, I need to be ca
reful about the scope. The PR title/branch is `design/issue-19` which is specifi
cally about UIPanel, UIDialog, UIToast, UIAlert. However, the PR touches many mo
re files. The design-spec.md for issue-19 explicitly says in section 9.5: "无魔
